          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Maritime Industries Relief Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Tariff Act of 1930 to exempt from duty certain pre-owned vessels offered for sale or sold in the United States. It repeals the deferral until sale of the duty on large yachts imported for sale at U.S. boat shows.</p>]]></text>
